  "root_text": {
    "iti73:0.1": "Itivuttaka 73 ",
    "iti73:0.2": "Tikanipāta ",
    "iti73:0.3": "Tatiyavagga ",
    "iti73:0.4": "Santatarasutta ",
    "iti73:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti73:2.1": "“Rūpehi, bhikkhave, arūpā santatarā, arūpehi nirodho santataro”ti. ",
    "iti73:2.2": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti73:2.3": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti73:3.1": "“Ye ca rūpūpagā sattā, ",
    "iti73:3.2": "ye ca arūpaṭṭhāyino; ",
    "iti73:3.3": "Nirodhaṁ appajānantā, ",
    "iti73:3.4": "āgantāro punabbhavaṁ. ",
    "iti73:4.1": "Ye ca rūpe pariññāya, ",
    "iti73:4.2": "arūpesu asaṇṭhitā; ",
    "iti73:4.3": "Nirodhe ye vimuccanti, ",
    "iti73:4.4": "te janā maccuhāyino. ",
    "iti73:5.1": "Kāyena amatadhātuṁ, ",
    "iti73:5.2": "phusayitvā nirūpadhiṁ; ",
    "iti73:5.3": "Upadhippaṭinissaggaṁ, ",
    "iti73:5.4": "sacchikatvā anāsavo; ",
    "iti73:5.5": "Deseti sammāsambuddho, ",
    "iti73:5.6": "asokaṁ virajaṁ padan”ti. ",
    "iti73:6.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti73:6.2": "Catutthaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti73:0.1": "So It Was Said 73 ",
    "iti73:0.2": "The Book of the Threes ",
    "iti73:0.3": "Chapter Three ",
    "iti73:0.4": "More Peaceful ",
    "iti73:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti73:2.1": "“Mendicants, formless states are more peaceful than states of form; cessation is more peaceful than formless states.” ",
    "iti73:2.2": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti73:2.3": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti73:3.1": "“There are beings in the realm of luminous form, ",
    "iti73:3.2": "and others stuck in the formless. ",
    "iti73:3.3": "Not understanding cessation, ",
    "iti73:3.4": "they return in future lives. ",
    "iti73:4.1": "But the people who completely understand form, ",
    "iti73:4.2": "not stuck in the formless, ",
    "iti73:4.3": "released in cessation—",
    "iti73:4.4": "they are conquerors of death. ",
    "iti73:5.1": "Having directly experienced <j>the element free of death, ",
    "iti73:5.2": "free of attachments; ",
    "iti73:5.3": "having realised relinquishment ",
    "iti73:5.4": "of attachments, the undefiled ",
    "iti73:5.5": "fully awakened Buddha teaches ",
    "iti73:5.6": "the sorrowless, stainless state.” ",
    "iti73:6.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
  "variant_text": {
    "iti73:3.2": "arūpaṭṭhāyino → āruppaṭhāyino (bj) "
  },
